    school_title1: 'We build courses that students and teachers love',
    school_des11: 'Our LMS provides a wide variety of interactive tasks, perfect for self-study or classroom use.',
    school_des12: 'Full lesson plans are provided for teachers with games and fun activities for every lesson, saving preparation time and making sure your English program is popular and successful.',
    school_des13: 'Our AI-assisted marking system saves teachers even more time and gives students detailed reports and progress tracking, including uploaded texts, video and audio files for every speaking or writing task.',
    school_title2: 'Give your students the highest-quality exam preparation',
    school_des21: 'We provide tailor-made courses for all the major examinations, with any blend of classroom and online self-study required. We provide material to fit your needs, from online vocabulary builders and skills practice to full exam preparation courses. Lessons can be delivered by your teachers, our consultants, or both.',
    school_des22: 'Teachers are supported with full lesson plans and exam training, enabling them to provide the best practice and assessment.',
    school_des23: 'We use AI to provide avatars for extensive speaking practice and automated marking, making focused exam preparation thorough and cost-efficient.',
    school_title3: 'Attract new and foreign students with special courses',
    school_des31: 'We can build special courses to attract new students, branded to your school.',
    school_des32: 'These can be courses to help them make friends and settle in the community, or courses to help them develop a particular language skill.',
    school_des33: 'We also provide innovative courses for parents to develop their own English with their child. Parents can study on our app while their child learns in school, then they can enjoy fun practice activities together.',
    school_title4: 'Maintain the highest standards, develop an international program and save money on recruitment with our teacher training courses',
    school_des41: 'Our TEFL courses give teachers the tools they need to plan and deliver fun and effective language lessons.',
    school_des42: 'Our EMI (English Medium Instruction) courses enable schools to develop an international program and deliver all subjects in English.',
    school_des43: 'Our EAP (English for Academic Purposes) programs help teachers prepare students to specific exams and academic skills.',
    school_des44: 'With AI integrated into our App and our developer’s license with Open AI, we are at the forefront of teaching technology and incorporate this into all our teacher training courses.',
    school_des45: 'We also provide short AI workshops to update in-service teachers’ knowledge and make sure they are using the best tools.',
    school_title5: 'Increase revenue with our partnership programs',
    school_des51: 'Many schools have equal or superior facilities to private language schools but do not always provide the same courses and services. A partnership with us can instantly solve this problem.',
    school_des52: 'From after-school programs for kids, to evening classes for adults, we provide a complete package: high-quality courses, digital and hard-copy materials, full lesson plans and teacher training. You simply provide the facilities you already have: classrooms, basic stationery and student services.',
    school_des53: 'Through our contacts with examination centres and extensive experience in assessment and materials development, we can quickly adopt and deliver the most relevant and popular examinations.',
    school_des54: 'Our tailor-made courses can also help you open up new classes to serve the local community, such as Business English for managers and business owners, Technical English for workers, and Communication Skills for those learning for pleasure or social integration.',
    school_des55: 'Together, we can quickly produce high-quality and fun courses to rival any language school, keep your students happy and open new revenue streams.',
    school_title6: 'Benefits',
    school_des61: 'Build your reputation and attract new students',
    school_des62: 'High-quality teaching with fun activities in every class.',
    school_des63: 'Flexible learning options with our user-friendly App.',
    school_des64: 'Tailor-made courses and special promotions.',
