    school_des66: 'Budget Savings',
    school_des67: 'Reduce preparation and marking costs with full lesson plans and AI-assisted marking and reports.',
    school_des68: 'Reduce native-speaker teaching costs with AI avatars.',
    school_des69: 'Make huge savings on teacher training with discounted courses from Cambridge-approved teacher trainers.',
